'''Braai''' (Bêša nama) ke neano tsoang sechabeng e leng lipuo tseo nama pele ko Grill kapa Météo pheha holim 'a mashala se chesa ka golo. Neano ea lona qalong o ile a qala le tša Maburu (Afrikaners),<ref name="Osseo-Asare">{{cite book|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=1s-a7EMM6BgC|title=Food Culture in Sub-Saharan Africa|author=Fran Osseo-Asare|pages=81|isbn=0-313-32488-3|publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group|date=2005}}</ref> empa na wa tloha ha namela wa batho ba bang kao fela ba [[Afrika Borwa]], wa akarelletsa le [[Botswana]], [[Namibia]], [[Lesotho]], [[Zimbabwe]] le [[Zambia]].

Ntle ho moo disementshisi nama, poone, ditapole a foil 'me li-mushroom ka tloaelo sena halikiloeng, hangata e le lijana lehlakoreng la ka, empa ka linako tse ling e boetse e ka lokisoa joaloka lijong jeng nama.

Joaloka e bolelang boroso lentsoe, lentsoe Météo o boetse o akarelletsa [[Seisimane]] le lipuo tse ngata ka [[Borwa ba Afrika]].
